{"tid":2262241,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱症的變奏：心境惡劣障礙","createTime":"2020-10-29T03:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T15:57:50.000Z","uid":244168,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fbfc370c6626c4ded2ddd733d1c454ba76b09f","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"有些朋友察覺自己有長期抑鬱症的症狀，在那可能不是抑鬱症，而是Dysthymia。想知更多，去片。<br />\n<br />\n其他關於精神醫學的問題也可以在這裏提出，答得到的會儘量回答。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MWhyr2aIbzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMWhyr2aIbzQ&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KimhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=ed1948c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MWhyr2aIbzQ</a>"},{"pid":"6ff0ed289c3575e01c52195e2e1dd122460cf8d0","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c834ee394581caab7ac004a704026a632442427","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb959a49aeb79e2ccca0b26741246bf5dd228c8b","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e1e16894d2a42fbfd5b3dd04aed7a0fb53d7ddd","tid":2262241,"uid":282718,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"如果係呢一類應該要點處理？定當無野？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他們有時候會看東西看得很負面<br />\n有很多生活上的小事<br />\n他也會看到是很嚴重<br />\n讓自己很困擾&rdquo;<br />\n其實咁樣算唔算焦慮？<br />\n<br />\n支持小鳥醫生 希望可以分享多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21b862203e0816f2156265d1a91d5da4e01dec0","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"9e1e16894d2a42fbfd5b3dd04aed7a0fb53d7ddd","tid":2262241,"uid":282718,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"如果係呢一類應該要點處理？定當無野？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他們有時候會看東西看得很負面<br />\n有很多生活上的小事<br />\n他也會看到是很嚴重<br />\n讓自己很困擾&rdquo;<br />\n其實咁樣算唔算焦慮？<br />\n<br />\n支持小鳥醫生 希望可以分享多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"其實對於這一類病人<br />\n雖然也可以使用抗抑鬱藥<br />\n但根據小鳥醫生的經驗<br />\n成效不是太過顯著<br />\n<br />\n因為他們的問題大多是psychological而不是Biological<br />\n就像面對同一件事<br />\n他們會有不同的bias<br />\n就像他們被問到最近在做些什麼，他們可能會覺得別人在笑他們失業<br />\n或者每做一件事情，即使是在開始的階段，他們總是認為最終必定失敗<br />\n<br />\n我認為認知行為治療對這類病人應該有些幫助<br />\n或者比較新的mindfulness治療可以讓他們活在當下，用另一副眼鏡去看世界"},{"pid":"feb19cab468122a24bfb905d680ca4efe5c8399a","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0087357ea74e8a31b3c88e665293fa3f81f74a48","tid":2262241,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cb8e55e1c121b62094212a79ab53beefdb8cdaa3","tid":2262241,"uid":161163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7c5f279935042ea851d2754a6e0ccedd98d42fc2","tid":2262241,"uid":97811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"support! liked and subscribed!"},{"pid":"29f3f85c8a768fff5d3057774440f62a1e6e6369","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c5f279935042ea851d2754a6e0ccedd98d42fc2","tid":2262241,"uid":97811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"support! liked and subscribed!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"Thank you !"},{"pid":"8ea3ca34b0bb32a98b1620bdce0036cbb936ea5e","tid":2262241,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e8791c5668108a07816746d12dc4765fd32b0f","tid":2262241,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike