br />\ndiagnosis祇不過係等醫生醫嘅時候方便一啲<br />\n但係最重要嘅其實係一個病嘅formulation<br />\n就係一個病點樣產生佢背後有啲咩原因<br />\n可以係細個時候嘅一啲遭遇，父母親離異，返學被欺淩，兄弟姊妹之間嘅鬥爭，乜都有可能<br />\n解決得到嘅事情，解決咗自然唔會病<br />\n但係有時解決唔到嘅心結，即使解決唔到，但係病人Acknowledge得到係同自己嘅某啲想法有關係，都會有所幫助"},{"pid":"1b090465acdf80c3ffc8152ded49f0439178ffb7","tid":2262241,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c25ce386bcf7d14a708ddfab3cb879cdffd8ea1","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"謝謝"},{"pid":"7d4719c188361c3556ae43a803ee7a1b1be12d77","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"979e1d30385c596c8cf7d4bf341b048ac8a7e914","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdd17980cea1e561770bcc864b8f5e1e370cbcc3","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"明天早上11時將會播出第3集"},{"pid":"0791c9f27b87258385a0aa3b8801570dda63d7bf","tid":2262241,"uid":218374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"想請問下小鳥醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據我印象，醫生冇好確實話我有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但自從我出現情緒低落、冇乜動力<br />\n甚至乎出現自殺念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生9月中開咗Lexapro 25mg<br />\n由半粒，變成食一粒<br />\n因為持續維持低落情緒、亦有自殺念頭<br />\n然後10月中轉藥，分別係Pristiq 25mg、Pristiq 50mg同PMS-Quetiapine 25mg。<br />\n依架就繼續食多兩星期嘅Pristiq 50mg同PMS-Quetiapine 25mg⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n講真我食藥食到怕..雖然食咗Q仔俾未食之前肯定好瞓啲，但瞓醒有時都好攰，好想繼續瞓...覺得好絕望<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀...講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk