":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e7381f95d8c9b8682dbe4df83a8cd101d2bb7c","tid":2262241,"uid":256291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"咁嘅情況，兩邊都睇啦"},{"pid":"c5911dd493f800a4654ec0d4796e017ad591849f","tid":2262241,"uid":218374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2343f35c18bc9bfef2e74091b18762f446b627a7","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0791c9f27b87258385a0aa3b8801570dda63d7bf","tid":2262241,"uid":218374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"想請問下小鳥醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據我印象，醫生冇好確實話我有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但自從我出現情緒低落、冇乜動力<br />\n甚至乎出現自殺念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生9月中開咗Lexapro 25mg<br />\n由半粒，變成食一粒<br />\n因為持續維持低落情緒、亦有自殺念頭<br />\n然後10月中轉藥，分別係Pristiq 25mg、Pristiq 50mg同PMS-Quetiapine 25mg。<br />\n依架就繼續食多兩星期嘅Pristiq 50mg同PMS-Quetiapine 25mg⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n講真我食藥食到怕..雖然食咗Q仔俾未食之前肯定好瞓啲，但瞓醒有時都好攰，好想繼續瞓...覺得好絕望<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀...講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"Pristiq主要用來增加動力，如果10月中轉藥，可能仲需要少少時間，仲有50mg仲有增加嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\nquetiapine咁嘅劑量其實都係俾你瞓覺，如果之後瞓覺好咗其實未必需要食。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:32:36.000Z","msg":"我想問Pristiq同Quetiapine長期咁食有咩副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者本身帶有咩副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋增加劑量個反應會係點？"},{"pid":"fac47d173dd5cf2acd4d2ef133548836227a5f73","tid":2262241,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5911dd493f800a4654ec0d4796e017ad5